{"tid":1551403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教畜睇路 民賤聯搞監師會","createTime":"2019-09-08T03:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:35:32.000Z","uid":115613,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9432334a2eb13637bd0a99acead47e5f25e646","tid":1551403,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:53:48.000Z","msg":"民建聯偕警察家屬晤3局長　反對獨立調查促設「監師會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190907/s00001/1567855334885/【逃犯條例】民建聯偕警察家屬晤3局長-反對獨立調查促設「監師會」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F1567855334885%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E5%81%95%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E6%99%A43%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E4%BF%83%E8%A8%AD%E3%80%8C%E7%9B%A3%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8D&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkproeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=691890a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190907%2Fs00001%2F1567855334885%2F%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E5%81%95%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E6%99%A43%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7-%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E4%BF%83%E8%A8%AD%E3%80%8C%E7%9B%A3%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83%E3%80%8D&h=7b60b079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190907/s00001/1567855334885/【逃犯條例】民建聯偕警察家屬晤3局長-反對獨立調查促設「監師會」</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員李慧琼、葛珮帆今日（7日）聯同一班警察家屬，與保安局長李家超、教育局長楊潤雄和公務員事務局長羅智光見面。警察家屬向3名局長提出多項訴求，包括強烈反對成立獨立調查委員會，要求教育局成立「監師會」和在課室設置錄影及錄音設備，需要時作參考。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n15個警察及紀律部隊宿舍代表向3名局長發出聯署信，稱社會近日暴力事件愈趨嚴重，令不少警務人員身心受創，承受不公平對待及無理指摘。他們希望改善香港教育問題，以及警隊成員和家屬的不公平待遇。<br />\n<br />\n他們提出10多項訴求，包括向李家超提出冀加快推動「侮辱公職人員罪」及「蒙面法」立法；為警隊爭取更多資源，提供足夠支援，維持警隊士氣。他們又要求成立針對大型示威等特別事故聯合紀律部隊，包括警隊、消防、懲教、海關、入境和飛行服務隊等人員。<br />\n<br />\n他們對楊潤雄提出，必須成立「監師會」，監督教師並提交調查報告予教育局，再根據報告內容設懲處及扣分機制；要求禁止仇視言論、教師教學要保持中立態度；課室設置錄影及錄音設備；以及將中國歷史科目列入必修科，重新檢視通識科課程及課本內容。<br />\n<br />\n他們又向羅智光要求恢復警察福利，包括公務員海外教育津貼及本地教育津貼，以及必須增設內地教育津貼計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班食公務員糧既土皇帝 監師會成立之後會monitor 實你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5021061dfe6458bd3609c0a5daae3c8ba25ff7","tid":1551403,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"「懷疑有組織發佈大量fake news想搞散場抗爭」<br />\n做人要有公關！文宣多一個就好多！連儂牆要人！<br />\n<br />\n今日 下午 美國領事館 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，生活中抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制「邪惡」「無良」的商戶，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests <br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkproeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=6e9d9837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour ，五毛分化post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.08"},{"pid":"1d3114d33c8b4460653ae41c76c53d17bf433174","tid":1551403,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T03:57:48.000Z","msg":"人民日報：不能縱容「恐怖教師」<br />\n<br />\n另外，《人民日報》海外版昨日刊登文章表示，學校應教育學生愛國愛港，不能縱容教師和學生反中亂港；又質疑香港教師資格審查制度，或存在嚴重缺陷，教協維權不能無底線，不能縱容「恐怖教師」；教育局不能擔心得罪某些「恐怖教師」及背後勢力而放棄監管職責。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">教畜睇路la</span></span>"},{"pid":"360f477f9e999ea6d3614cb5100f139755b3bd5e","tid":1551403,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEN3JB5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEEN3JB5.png&h=9190afe0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a53e7ecc98076a993a72135162e9251c9f1c225","tid":1551403,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"360f477f9e999ea6d3614cb5100f139755b3bd5e","tid":1551403,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEN3JB5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEEN3JB5.png&h=9190afe0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:02:44.000Z","msg":"JM9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87edd08fd9140a2c77d69302bea41c589ffb7950","tid":1551403,"uid":79278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"你標題仲用教畜 真係唔知你做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n課室有cam 最驚一定唔係老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最驚個班肯定係 公開試0分考警個班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.